Package: gmstools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Online Wildlife Trade Monitoring and Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Russell",
           family = "Gray",
           email = "russell.gray@globalinitiative.net",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolkit developed for the Global Monitoring System (GMS) to streamline the detection, analysis, and visualization of online illegal wildlife trade data. Includes standardized functions for data cleaning, flag plots, platform-specific trend analysis, quadrant movement tracking, and model diagnostics. Built for consistent use across GMS Data Hub investigations and law enforcement intelligence reports.
